{"tid":1794185,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"美團否認外賣員因差評殺人：以警方通報為準","createTime":"2019-12-23T02:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T05:08:58.000Z","uid":53062,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f60ec461039b6b183f0953182d23af35ae83d4da","tid":1794185,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpbSE1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpbSE1a.jpg&h=54028d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWLgne7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWLgne7.jpg&h=034b3fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12月22日下午，在武漢洪山區的佰港城商城發生了一起殺人案，美團的外賣小哥持刀殺死一人，隨後被捕。 對於殺人的原因，網絡傳聞稱美團小哥是因為收到了顧客的差評，憤怒之下殺人，不過這一說話被美團否認。<br />\n<br />\n 美觀點評公關部相關人士在給媒體的聲明中否認事件與外賣小哥的差評有關，不過美團也沒有公佈外賣小哥的具體動機，強調事件已經有警方介入，具體信息以警方通報為準 。<br />\n<br />\n此前，洪山平安發表通告，稱&ldquo;12月22日下午2時許，洪山公安接到群眾報警：南湖佰港城有人持刀傷人。派出所、警務站民警迅速趕到現場，與安保力量合力 將行凶嫌疑人控制。經120急救人員對受傷男子檢查發現其已無生命體徵。<br />\n<br />\n 經查，受害人系佰港城員工，嫌疑人為外賣配送員陳某（男，32歲）。 雙方發生口角，陳某持刀將周某刺倒。 案件正在進一步審理之中。  &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得罪外賣仔仲想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8044135b93a3bd6af8b1c35e74d5d5e89a4d619","tid":1794185,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01c8068d84c2931db9871e662d1e2697088966bb","tid":1794185,"uid":686